Package: fastboot-tcp
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: Tom Dewey <tom.dewey@raspberrypi.com>
Depends: rpi-fastbootd (>= 14)
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Description: Systemd service for fastboot over TCP
 Runs rpi-fastbootd in TCP mode for network-based device provisioning.
 Starts after network-online.target and restarts automatically on failure.
